 Ah I see the issue now - you are getting that error because RedisTransport is not being imported correctly.

Instead of:

```js
const RedisTransport = require('winston-redis').Redis;
```

It should be:

```js 
const { RedisTransport } = require('winston-redis');
```

The full code would be:

```js
const redis = require('redis');
const { RedisTransport } = require('winston-redis');

const redisClient = redis.createClient({
  host: 'localhost', 
  port: 6379
});

const redisTransport = new RedisTransport({
  client: redisClient  
});
```

The key is to import RedisTransport using destructuring assignment from the winston-redis module.

